data.description: Pristine 2-bed, 2.5-bath end unit townhome with a main floor master suite. Open floorplan with tons of natural light!  White kitchen includes tile backsplash, dining area and overlooks the spacious family room. Both bedrooms boast private full baths and walk-in closets. Plus, there's a convenient half bath on the first floor. Outside, you'll find a charming patio area, ideal for alfresco dining, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air. The Community amenities include swimming and tennis facilities. Enjoy a newer HVAC system installed and a brand-new water heater. Motivated seller willing to assist with 2-1 buydown. Don't miss this great property!
